### Notation:
$\vec{a}+\vec{b}$

# Formula/Algebraically:
$$\begin{bmatrix}a\\b\end{bmatrix}+ \begin{bmatrix}A\\B\end{bmatrix}=\begin{bmatrix}a+A\\b+B\end{bmatrix}$$
